title: Glen Cook Collection
description:
This is a collection of 43 Glen Cook novels and 10 short stories (all in .doc format). 

The Black Company (all 10 novels)
The Dark War Trilogy
The Dread Empire series
All 11 Garrett novels
The Starfishes series
The first Instrumentalities of the Night novel

Standalone novels include: A Matter of Time, And Dragons in the Sky, Sung In Blood, The Dragon Never Sleeps, The Heirs of Babylon, The Swordbearer, The Tower of Fear.
